#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chi Industries combat headset"
msgid_plural "Chi Industries combat headsets"
msgstr[0] "奇工业战斗耳机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chi Industries combat headset'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chi Industries combat headset (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Chi Industries combat headsets (active)'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"The Chi Industries combat headset is a target aquisition system designed for"
" use with the Chi-93b gaiden power suit. Lacks a great deal of ballistic "
"effectiveness due to lack of coverage around the head."
msgstr "奇工业战斗耳机是一款目标捕获系统，专为搭配奇-93b外传动力装甲使用而设计。由于头部覆盖范围不足，其弹道防护效果较为有限。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chi Industries combat headset (active)"
msgid_plural "Chi Industries combat headsets (active)"
msgstr[0] "奇工业战斗耳机（已激活）"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chi Industries power armor"
msgid_plural "Chi Industries power armors"
msgstr[0] "奇工业动力装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chi Industries power armor'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"This rather unique variant of power armor was developed by the famed "
"Japanese robot company, Chi Industries. Known as the Chi-93b Gaiden power "
"suit, this armor sacrifices protection for increased manuevarability and "
"decreased cost. Curiously, the armor comes in two sex-based variants: an "
"armored anime-esque battledress for women, and a more conventional form of "
"power armor for men."
msgstr ""
"这款相当独特的动力装甲变体由著名的日本机器人公司奇工业开发。它被称为奇-93b外传动力装甲，牺牲了部分防护以换取更高的机动性和更低的成本。有趣的是，该装甲提供两种基于性别的变体：为女性设计的装甲动漫风格战服，以及为男性设计的更传统形式的动力装甲。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chi Industries power armor (active)"
msgid_plural "Chi Industries power armors (active)"
msgstr[0] "奇工业动力装甲（已激活）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chi Industries power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Chi Industries power armors (active)'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"This rather unique variant of power armor was developed by the famed "
"Japanese robot company, Chi Industries. Known as the Chi-93b Gaiden power "
"suit, this armor sacrifices protection for increased manuevarability and "
"decreased cost. Curiously, the armor comes in two sex-based variants: an "
"armored anime-esque battledress for women, and a more conventional form of "
"power armor for men.  It is currently turned on, activate it to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"这款相当独特的动力装甲变体由著名的日本机器人公司奇工业开发。它被称为奇-93b外传动力装甲，牺牲了部分防护以换取更高的机动性和更低的成本。有趣的是，该装甲提供两种基于性别的变体：为女性设计的装甲动漫风格战服，以及为男性设计的更传统形式的动力装甲。当前已启动，激活可将其关闭。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "XEDRA excursion suit"
msgid_plural "XEDRA excursion suits"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA探险服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XEDRA excursion suit'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"Developed by XEDRA for use in the most hazardous environments, the excursion"
" suit is a seldom seen, and even more seldom used power armor unit. Unlike "
"most power armor units, the excursion suit features a relatively large "
"internal storage area for jaunts across the New England exclusion zone, or "
"perhaps areas more extra-terrestrial in nature."
msgstr ""
"由XEDRA开发，用于最危险的环境，探险服是一种罕见且更少使用的动力装甲单元。与大多数动力装甲单元不同，探险服配备了一个相对较大的内部存储区域，适合在新英格兰隔离区或可能更具外星性质的地带进行短途旅行。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "XEDRA excursion suit (active)"
msgid_plural "XEDRA excursion suits (active)"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA探险服（已激活）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XEDRA excursion suit (active)', 'str_pl': 'XEDRA
#. excursion suits (active)'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"Developed by XEDRA for use in the most hazardous environments, the excursion"
" suit is a seldom seen, and even more seldom used power armor unit. Unlike "
"most power armor units, the excursion suit features a relatively large "
"internal storage area for jaunts across the New England exclusion zone, or "
"perhaps areas more extra-terrestrial in nature.  It is currently turned on, "
"activate it to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"由XEDRA开发，用于最危险的环境，探险服是一种罕见且更少使用的动力装甲单元。与大多数动力装甲单元不同，探险服配备了一个相对较大的内部存储区域，适合在新英格兰隔离区或可能更具外星性质的地带进行短途旅行。当前已启动，激活可将其关闭。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "XEDRA excursion suit helmet"
msgid_plural "XEDRA excursion suit helmets"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA探险服头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XEDRA excursion suit helmet'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XEDRA excursion suit helmet (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'XEDRA excursion suit helmets (active)'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"A fully enclosed combat helmet for hazardous environments, features a large "
"transparent superalloy visor similar to those found on spacesuits.  The "
"environmental controls function best with direct-skin contact. It's target-"
"acquisition visor slightly improves the user's perception."
msgstr ""
"一款为危险环境设计的全封闭式战斗头盔，配备类似宇航服的大型透明超级合金面罩。环境控制系统在直接皮肤接触时效果最佳。其目标捕获面罩略微提升了使用者的感知能力。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "XEDRA excursion suit helmet (active)"
msgid_plural "XEDRA excursion suit helmets (active)"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA探险服头盔（已激活）"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chinese jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "Chinese jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "中国连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chinese jumpsuit'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"A kevlar-infused jumpsuit intended to be employed by members of the Chinese "
"armed forces. Rather form-fitting."
msgstr "一款注入凯夫拉纤维的连体服，旨在供中国武装部队成员使用。相当贴身。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chinese Stealth jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "Chinese Stealth jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "中国隐形连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chinese Stealth jumpsuit'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"A kevlar-infused stealth suit intended to be employed by members of the "
"Chinese armed forces. Rather form-fitting. The suit distorts rays of light "
"before they make contact with the suit, allowing the user to more easily "
"evade attacks."
msgstr "一款注入凯夫拉纤维的隐形服，旨在供中国武装部队成员使用。相当贴身。该服装在光线接触服装前将其扭曲，使使用者更容易躲避攻击。"

#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "Newt Mk.I"
msgid_plural "Newt Mk.Is"
msgstr[0] "纽特Mk.I"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Newt Mk.I'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"Originally designed as a bipedal scout robot for private contractors, the "
"Newt has found a wide variety of uses both within the military and the "
"civilian world. It's most famous fixture is its large bio-synthetic legs "
"that constitute most of its mass. Those legs are for more than just walking "
"though, a kick from a Newt can easily break a man's ribs."
msgstr ""
"纽特最初设计为私人承包商的双足侦察机器人，后来在军事和民用领域发现了广泛的用途。其最著名的特点是构成其大部分质量的大型生物合成腿。这些腿不仅仅用于行走，纽特的一踢足以轻易折断人的肋骨。"

#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "broken Newt Mk.I"
msgid_plural "broken Newt Mk.Is"
msgstr[0] "损坏的纽特Mk.I"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Newt Mk.I'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Newt Mk.II'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"A broken Newt Mk.I, now wrecked and motionless. Synthetic blood still oozes "
"from its muscular legs. It could be gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一台损坏的纽特Mk.I，现已残破且静止不动。合成血液仍从其肌肉发达的腿部渗出。可将其拆解以获取备用零件。"

#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "inactive Newt Mk.I"
msgid_plural "inactive Newt Mk.Is"
msgstr[0] "未激活的纽特Mk.I"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive Newt Mk.I'}
