msgid "An inactive Newt Mk.I."
msgstr "一台未激活的纽特Mk.I。"

#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "Newt Mk.II"
msgid_plural "Newt Mk.IIs"
msgstr[0] "纽特Mk.II"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Newt Mk.II'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"Originally designed as a bipedal scout robot for private contractors, the "
"Newt has found a wide variety of uses both within the military and the "
"civilian world. It's most famous fixture is its large bio-synthetic legs "
"that constitute most of its mass. Those legs are for more than just walking "
"though, a kick from a Newt can easily break a man's ribs. This variant has "
"received a suite of upgrades, slightly improving its speed and damage "
"resistance."
msgstr ""
"纽特最初设计为私人承包商的双足侦察机器人，后来在军事和民用领域发现了广泛的用途。其最著名的特点是构成其大部分质量的大型生物合成腿。这些腿不仅仅用于行走，纽特的一踢足以轻易折断人的肋骨。此变体经过一系列升级，略微提升了速度和伤害抗性。"

