#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "police gynoid"
msgid_plural "police gynoids"
msgstr[0] "警用女性机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'police gynoid'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"In a radical departure from form, New England Law enforcement decided to "
"procure an overseas robotic frame with a far less disturbing appearance than"
" their standard models. After seeking a variety of offers, The Chi "
"Industries Model P-013 series service gynoid was chosen. Don't let their "
"appearance fool you, these robots are no less dangerous than their less-"
"humanoid counterparts. This one is equipped with a police baton."
msgstr ""
"新英格兰执法部门一反常态，决定采购一种海外机器人框架，其外观远比标准型号更不令人不安。在寻求多种方案后，奇工业 P-013 "
"系列服务型女性机器人被选中。别被它们的外表欺骗，这些机器人的危险性丝毫不亚于那些不那么像人的同类。此型号配备了一支警棍。"

#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "broken police gynoid"
msgid_plural "broken police gynoids"
msgstr[0] "损坏的警用女性机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken police gynoid'}
