msgstr[0] "多功能机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Utili-Bot'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"The Chi Industries Utili-bot was designed as the famous consumer electronics"
" company's first foray into consumer robotics. Around the size of a family "
"dog, the Utilibot was intended as a general purpose platform for domestic "
"duties, daily chores and even companionship (although that wasn't very "
"likely). The Utili-bot was a product that divided people into two camps: "
"either you saw the robot as a decadent pile of electronic trash, or as an "
"invaluable and tireless servant."
msgstr ""
"奇工业多功能机器人是这家著名消费电子公司首次涉足消费机器人领域的尝试。大小约如家犬，多功能机器人旨在作为通用平台，用于家庭职责、日常杂务甚至陪伴（尽管这不太可能）。这款产品将人们分为两个阵营：要么视其为颓废的电子垃圾堆，要么视其为无价且不知疲倦的仆人。"

