#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ZX-19'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"The ZX-19 is a chinese military drone designed for use as an automated "
"platoon-level logistics and auxilliary support platform. Similar to its "
"american counterpart, it took design cues from nature, and features four "
"stout legs to help it trot around the field of battle. This particular "
"variant is equipped with a 9mm gun turret. How it was deployed to New "
"England, and exactly when, is unknown."
msgstr ""
"ZX-19是一款中国军用无人机，设计用作自动化排级后勤与辅助支援平台。与它的美国同类相似，其设计灵感源于自然，并配备四条粗壮的腿，以帮助它在战场上小跑移动。此特定型号装备有一挺9毫米机枪炮塔。它是如何以及何时被部署到新英格兰地区的，目前尚不清楚。"

