#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Zhuazi N-1'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"The Zhuazi N-1 is a unmanned ground vehicle that was rumored to exist on the"
" dark corners of internet before the Cataclysm, confirmed to be very real "
"only relatively recently. When they are not deployed, Zhuazi drones look "
"similar to large ballistic shells, and only deploy their legs after they've "
"impacted the ground after falling in a ballistic arc from beyond the "
"horizon. The mechanical feet act as spades, and are also sufficiently sharp "
"to damage any would-be assailant."
msgstr ""
"爪子N-1是一种无人地面载具，在大灾变前曾传闻存在于互联网的阴暗角落，直到相对近期才被证实确实存在。当它们未被部署时，爪子无人机看起来类似于大型弹道炮弹，只有在从地平线外以弹道弧线坠落撞击地面后才会展开腿部。其机械足充当铲子，同时也足够锋利，足以伤害任何潜在的袭击者。"

