#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XEDRA Newt Mk.I'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"Originally designed as a bipedal scout robot for private contractors, the "
"Newt has found a wide variety of uses both within the military and the "
"civilian world. It's most famous fixture is its large bio-synthetic legs "
"that constitute most of its mass. Those legs are for more than just walking "
"though, a kick from a Newt can easily break a man's ribs. This variant has "
"been deployed by XEDRA, seemingly after the cataclysm was well underway. It "
"is equipped with deployable blades on its mechanical feet, giving it extra "
"cutting damage."
msgstr ""
"纽特最初被设计为私人承包商使用的双足侦察机器人，后来在军事和民用领域都找到了广泛的用途。它最著名的特点是其巨大的生物合成腿部，构成了其大部分质量。这些腿不仅仅用于行走，纽特的一脚轻易就能踢断人的肋骨。这个变体由XEDRA部署，似乎是在大灾变已经全面展开之后。它的机械脚上配备了可展开的刀刃，提供了额外的切割伤害。"

