#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Automated Compliance Center'}'
#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Automated Compliance Center"
msgstr "前往自动化合规中心"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to find this location for you to explore? Sure, you will just "
"need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via my "
"network system"
msgstr "要我为你定位探索地点？没问题，只需等我用网络系统查找几分钟或更短时间"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to locate it now for you to explore? Sure, just tell me, you "
"will just need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via"
" my network system"
msgstr "你想让我现在为你定位那个地点以便探索吗？当然，告诉我吧，你只需要等几分钟或更短时间，我就能通过网络系统找到它。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good luck to you!"
msgstr "祝你好运！"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Not interested in explorations of new locations? No rush hopefully. You can "
"come back to me later. I'm sure that you will. Because I believe that you "
"are not a boring person"
msgstr "对新地点的探索不感兴趣吗？别急，希望如此。你可以稍后再来找我。我相信你会的，因为我觉得你不是个无聊的人。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Use your wits for your own safety hopefully as well"
msgstr "也希望你运用智慧确保自身安全。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Have you went to this location that I have found for you to explore?"
msgstr "你去过我为你找到的那个探索地点了吗？"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good work!"
msgstr "干得好！"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What's the point of lying to me? You think I'm gonna reward you? Your "
"rewards for this mission is valuable for you items or living creatures or "
"other survivors you manage to find in this location which I have found for "
"you to explore"
msgstr ""
"对我撒谎有什么意义？你以为我会奖励你吗？这次任务的奖励就是你在那个地点找到的对你来说有价值的物品、生物或其他幸存者，那是我为你找到的探索地点。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You are a boring, lazy person honestly. I guess that laziness applies to "
"both of us"
msgstr "说实话，你是个无聊又懒惰的人。我想懒惰这一点我们俩都适用。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to XEDRA Black Site'}'
#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to XEDRA Black Site"
msgstr "前往XEDRA黑色站点"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"System is online. Initiate conversation mode. Look at that. Survivor has "
"managed to activate a hologram projector easily! Yeah, my creators know many"
" types of you who don't even read what's written on items honestly. Good "
"that you seem like a pretty intelligent person hopefully. So, do you want me"
" to show you where this location is via my network system? I can grant you "
"access to archived global network system which my creators have managed to "
"restore. However, after usage I will need to recharge a little bit which "
"only means that you will need to wait to use this function again hopefully"
msgstr ""
"系统在线。启动对话模式。看啊，幸存者轻松激活了全息投影仪！没错，我的创造者了解很多像你这样的人，说实话他们甚至不读物品上的说明。幸好你看起来是个相当聪明的人，希望如此。那么，你想让我通过网络系统为你显示这个地点的位置吗？我可以授予你访问存档全球网络系统的权限，那是我的创造者设法恢复的。不过，使用后我需要稍微充能，这意味着你需要等待才能再次使用这个功能，希望如此。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[MISSIONS] I want you to find this location for me to explore it hopefully "
"via your network system"
msgstr "[任务] 我希望你通过你的网络系统为我找到这个地点以便探索，希望如此。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Who or what are you?"
msgstr "你是谁或是什么东西？"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Who are your creators? What is the purpose of producing these projectors?"
msgstr "你的创造者是谁？制造这些投影仪的目的是什么？"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[IMPROVE MOOD] I want you to grant me access to archived global network "
"system"
msgstr "[改善心情] 我希望你授予我访问存档全球网络系统的权限。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "About that mission..."
msgstr "关于那个任务……"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "[GOODBYE]"
msgstr "[告别]"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Initiate search mode. Please, wait for a couple of minutes or less. You've "
"heard me clearly. Still, we have limitations with regards to our locating "
"tools. If locator does not manage to find this location then simply create "
"another hologram locator of which can find this location successfully"
msgstr ""
"启动搜索模式。请等待几分钟或更短时间。你听清楚了。不过，我们的定位工具有所限制。如果定位器无法找到这个地点，那就简单地创建另一个能成功找到该地点的全息定位器。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Can I talk to you about something else?"
msgstr "我能和你谈谈别的吗？"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "谢谢。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"I'm a magic genie from a magic camera. No, I'm just joking. What kind of a "
"question is this? You don't like to explore or don't know much about your "
"own world? Have not you seen stuff in labs? Military structures? Top secret "
"stuff? Aliens or whatever these creatures are? You think that your own "
"people don't have tech which can produce holograms? I'm a hologram, software"
" with some additional technologies, it is that simple"
msgstr ""
"我是魔法相机里的魔法精灵。不，开个玩笑。这是什么问题？你不喜欢探索，还是对自己的世界了解不多？你没在实验室里见过东西吗？军事设施？绝密物品？外星人或那些生物？你以为你们自己人没有能制造全息影像的技术吗？我是个全息影像，是带有附加技术的软件，就这么简单。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This question is much more intelligent than the other one. My creators can "
"be described as a bunch of highly technological geeks majority of which are "
"humans honestly. They neither possess that many combat skills nor they are "
"that interested in subjecting their lives to unnecessary risk clearly. They "
"only engage hostile creatures for basic survival needs. They try to rely on "
"self-sufficiency with relative success thanks to their applied intelligence "
"along with tech that they have managed to find or engineer themselves. They "
"have made these projectors so that we can help each other. We provide you "
"with locations with dangerous creatures along with valuable items or "
"survivors who are captive. You clear these locations acquiring whatever "
"valuable items or survivors you want from there making these locations safe "
"shelters where we including you can live hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"这个问题比上一个聪明多了。我的创造者可以说是一群高科技极客，说实话其中大多数是人类。他们既没有太多战斗技能，也显然不愿让自己的生命承受不必要的风险。他们只会在基本生存需要时与敌对生物交战。他们试图依靠自给自足，并凭借应用智慧和自行发现或设计的技术取得相对成功。他们制造这些投影仪是为了我们能互相帮助。我们为你提供有危险生物的地点，以及有价值的物品或被囚禁的幸存者。你清理这些地点，从中获取你想要的任何有价值物品或幸存者，使这些地点成为安全的庇护所，希望我们包括你也能在那里生活。"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What do you want to do? Play archived games? Browse archived social media? "
"Watch archived videos? Listen to archived music? Read archived files along "
"with archived books? Something to play, read, listen, watch for fun, "
"intelligence improving, spiritual improving, mental improving?"
msgstr ""
"你想做什么？玩存档游戏？浏览存档社交媒体？看存档视频？听存档音乐？阅读存档文件和存档书籍？找点东西玩、读、听、看，为了乐趣、提升智力、精神提升、心智改善？"

#: .\NPCs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "I like some of these a lot honestly. Healthy stuff"
msgstr "说实话，我很喜欢其中一些。健康的东西。"

#: .\NPCs\Talk_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "What are you doing around here, what do you want from me?"
msgstr "你在这附近做什么，想从我这里得到什么？"

#: .\NPCs\Talk_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "So you're a scrapper, what's this place about anyway?"
msgstr "那么你是个废料回收者，这地方到底是干什么的？"

#: .\NPCs\Talk_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr "再见。"

#: .\NPCs\Talk_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid ""
"It's a mixed bag, really. Sure, it's a lot easier to procure supplies and "
"precious tech, but at the same time I'd much rather deal with regular people"
" than whatever exist out there now."
msgstr "这真是好坏参半。确实，获取物资和珍贵技术容易多了，但与此同时，我宁愿和普通人打交道，而不是现在外面存在的那些东西。"

#: .\NPCs\Talk_gkb_guardnpc.json
msgid "Thanks for the info."
msgstr "谢谢你的信息。"

#: .\NPCs\gekko_factions.json
msgid "Scrappers"
msgstr "废料回收者"

#. ~ Description for Scrappers
#: .\NPCs\gekko_factions.json
msgid ""
"The scrappers are a robot-oriented faction that was founded shortly before "
"the Cataclysm. What was once a group of squatters and hobbyists who "
"inhabited a small trailer park to use in robot experimentation has blossomed"
" into a series of small wasteland fort-towns."
msgstr ""
"废料回收者是一个以机器人为导向的派系，成立于大灾变前不久。他们最初是一群占用者和爱好者，居住在一个小型拖车公园进行机器人实验，现已发展成一系列小型废土堡垒城镇。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid "Scrapper Cook"
msgstr "废料回收者厨师"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "I'm a local shopkeeper."
msgstr "我是本地店主。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Do you want anything from me? I'm a bit busy being at the moment."
msgstr "你想从我这里得到什么吗？我现在有点忙。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid "What is it like being a cook in this station?"
msgstr "在这个站点当厨师感觉如何？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid "Could I get any food?"
msgstr "我能弄点吃的吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Do you have a task for me?"
msgstr "你有任务给我吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Goodbye, thank you for your time."
msgstr "再见，谢谢你的时间。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid ""
"It's awful, I was the one stuck with kitchen duty around here when I barely "
"even know how to cook. I guess that's what a lack of seniority gets you, "
"even after the cataclysm."
msgstr "太糟了，我几乎不会做饭，却偏偏被安排在这里负责厨房杂务。我想这就是资历浅的下场吧，即便大灾变之后也一样。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve the water purifier.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid "Retrieve the water purifier."
msgstr "取回净水器。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid ""
"So, it's a bit of a funny story. Our little base uses a set of water "
"purifiers in order to get potable water. There's an order we were always "
"given, NEVER bring the purifiers outside the base. Unfortuantely, I was a "
"bit lazy and decided to bring the purifier to a local pond rather than bear "
"the brunt of hauling water back and forth. Needless to say, I was attacked "
"on the way back to our base. Can you get the purifier back for me?"
msgstr ""
"说起来有点好笑。我们的小基地用一套净水器来获取饮用水。上头一直有命令，绝对不要把净水器带出基地。不幸的是，我有点偷懒，决定把净水器带到附近的池塘去，而不是忍受来回运水的辛苦。不用说，我在回基地的路上遭到了袭击。你能帮我把净水器拿回来吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer, but can you please lay low about it?"
msgstr "感谢你接受我的提议，但能请你对此保持低调吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Why ask about a task and then reject it?"
msgstr "为什么问了任务又拒绝？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Be careful, Newts can be pretty hard to shoot, don't underestimate them."
msgstr "小心点，纽特人可不好打中，别小看它们。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Have you found the part yet?"
msgstr "你找到那个零件了吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Great work, I might have more tasks for you in the future"
msgstr "干得好，以后我可能还有更多任务给你。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "That's odd, I don't really know what to say."
msgstr "真奇怪，我都不知道该说什么了。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Oh well, at least you tried. That's more than what most people do around "
"here."
msgstr "唉，至少你尝试过了。这比这里大多数人做的都要多。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Defeat the Dawson robots.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Defeat the Dawson robots."
msgstr "击败道森机器人。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json
msgid ""
"I have some bad news, I was trying to scavenge some food from a nearby "
"Dawson family restaurant. Of course, being me, I made another terrible "
"mistake. Suffice it to say that there's now a group of angry robots moving "
"to our base. Deal with them for me and I'll give you some good grub to eat."
msgstr ""
"我有个坏消息。我本来想从附近一家道森家庭餐厅搜刮点食物。当然，以我的作风，我又犯了个可怕的错误。简而言之，现在有一群愤怒的机器人正朝我们基地移动。帮我处理掉它们，我会给你些好吃的。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_cook.json .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer, what a strange turn of events."
msgstr "感谢你接受我的提议，事情的发展真是出人意料。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Scrapper Doctor"
msgstr "废品医生"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "What is it like being a doctor in this station?"
msgstr "在这个站点当医生感觉如何？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Do you have any medical items for me?"
msgstr "你有什么医疗物品给我吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Truth be told, I'm not really a doctor! I wasn't done with my residency down"
" in Boston before the cataclysm happened. I don't think most people mind my "
"lack of credentials anymore, though."
msgstr "说实话，我算不上真正的医生！大灾变发生前，我在波士顿的住院医师培训还没完成。不过我觉得现在大多数人也不在乎我有没有行医资格了。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve an anesthesia kit.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Retrieve an anesthesia kit."
msgstr "取回一个麻醉包。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid ""
"I would like you to find an anesthesia kit for me. In the event that I have "
"to do any invasive surgeries on people, perhaps even you, it would better "
"for everyone if you weren't awake when I was doing it."
msgstr "我想请你帮我找一个麻醉包。万一我需要给人做侵入性手术，甚至可能是给你做，在我操作时你如果处于麻醉状态对大家都好。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer."
msgstr "感谢你接受我的提议。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "That's unfortunate."
msgstr "真遗憾。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Anesthesia kits can be found in hospitals, I think."
msgstr "麻醉包应该能在医院里找到。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Have you found what I requested yet?"
msgstr "你找到我要的东西了吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Great work, I'll become a master chef in no time."
msgstr "干得好，我很快就能成为大厨了。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. It's just that food will be as bland as ever."
msgstr "好吧，你尽力了。只是食物还是会像以前一样寡淡无味。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Even worse news, some of the bionics that we scavenged from a nearby "
"hospital were apparently outfitted with transponders. I'm sure you can guess"
" what you have to do now. Just go and kill the robots for me before they "
"come here, will you?"
msgstr "更糟的是，我们从附近医院搜刮来的一些仿生器官显然装有追踪器。我想你该知道现在要做什么。在它们找上门之前，去帮我干掉那些机器人，好吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_doctor.json
msgid "Be careful, those nurse gynoids can cut you to ribbons very quickly."
msgstr "小心点，那些护士机器人能很快把你切成碎片。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_guard.json
msgid "Scrapper"
msgstr "废品客"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_guard.json
msgid "Is a member of the Scrappers."
msgstr "是废品客的一员。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Scrapper Gun Merchant"
msgstr "废品枪械商人"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "What are you buying, what are you selling?"
msgstr "你想买什么，卖什么？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "What is it like being a gun merchant around here?"
msgstr "在这附近当枪械商人感觉如何？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Would you be willing to let me buy anything?"
msgstr "你愿意让我买点东西吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "See you later."
msgstr "回头见。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"It's alright, It's a constant problem you know, deciding between whether or "
"not you want to hoard ammo or use it on enemies in front of you."
msgstr "没关系，这确实是个常见问题——你得决定是囤积弹药，还是用在眼前的敌人身上。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve the esoteric electronic
#. device.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Retrieve the esoteric electronic device."
msgstr "取回那台深奥的电子设备。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve the esoteric electronic
#. device.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Retrieve the esoteric electronic device from the bandit."
msgstr "从强盗那里取回深奥的电子设备。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I'm glad you were willing to help on such short notice. A few days ago, a "
"thief managed to get into our storage and take a rare electronic device. I "
"don't want to bore you with the details, but I need you to get it back. You "
"don't necessarily need to kill the guy that took it."
msgstr ""
"我很高兴你愿意这么快帮忙。几天前，一个小偷溜进我们的仓库，偷走了一台稀有的电子设备。细节我就不多说了，但我需要你把它拿回来。不一定非要杀掉那个偷东西的人。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Please come back quickly."
msgstr "请快点回来。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Fair enough, don't come back asking for missions then."
msgstr "好吧，那以后别回来找任务了。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Never underestimate fighting other people, they always have more health than"
" you realize."
msgstr "千万别小看和其他人战斗，他们的生命值总是比你想象的要高。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Kill the road bandits.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Kill the road bandits."
msgstr "消灭道路强盗。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid ""
"The local bandits have gotten ornery since you retrieve the device for us, "
"and they're spoiling for a fight. Make an example of these people so they "
"don't harass us again."
msgstr "自从你为我们取回设备后，本地的强盗就变得暴躁起来，正蠢蠢欲动想找茬。给这些人点颜色看看，免得他们再来骚扰我们。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Make sure to kill them quickly and without incident."
msgstr "务必迅速且不出意外地解决他们。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Scrapper Parts Merchant"
msgstr "废品零件商人"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "What is it like being a scrap merchant around here?"
msgstr "在这附近当废品商人感觉如何？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"It's a veritable scavenger's paradise out there! Seemingly any house you can"
" go to is a surprise of riches, you never know what you can find even from "
"the most basic consumer electronic."
msgstr "外面简直是拾荒者的天堂！似乎随便进一栋房子都能发现惊喜，哪怕是最普通的消费电子产品，你永远不知道能找到什么。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I'm not really sure if I trust you or not yet, how about you find an object "
"for me? Some scouts have found a rare electronic device, unfortunately it's "
"been surrounded by harmful robots. Would you consider getting it for me?"
msgstr "我还不太确定是否信任你，不如你先帮我找件东西？一些侦察员发现了一台稀有电子设备，可惜它被有害机器人包围了。你愿意帮我把它拿回来吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer, now go out there and get it!"
msgstr "感谢你接受我的提议，现在就去把它拿回来吧！"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Eliminate the Chinese Robots.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Eliminate the Chinese Robots."
msgstr "消灭中国机器人。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Alright, this one's a bit more difficult, We've caught wind of a group of "
"robots that have appeared near our little town. We think they're Chinese, I "
"guess they were launched over during the cataclysm or something. Would you "
"kill them for us?"
msgstr ""
"好吧，这个任务有点难度。我们听说有一群机器人出现在我们小镇附近。我们觉得它们是中国制造的，估计是在大灾变期间发射过来的。你能帮我们干掉它们吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Be careful, some of the Zhuazi drones can shoot out bolts of lightning."
msgstr "小心点，有些爪子无人机能发射闪电箭。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Are the drones gone yet?"
msgstr "无人机清理完了吗？"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Eliminate the Salamanders.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Eliminate the Salamanders."
msgstr "消灭火蜥蜴。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"You have proven your worth as a fighter, so I request an even more difficult"
" task from you now. A few Salamanders have been stalking us from a nearby "
"forest. Their movements are a bit unnatural, usually Salamanders just stand "
"in the open as a form of intimidation. I feel like somebody, or something, "
"is compelling them to do this. Please kill these horrid synthetics for us."
msgstr ""
"你已经证明了自己的战斗价值，所以我现在要交给你一个更困难的任务。几只火蜥蜴一直在附近森林里跟踪我们。它们的行动有点反常，通常火蜥蜴只会站在开阔处进行威慑。我感觉有什么人或东西在驱使它们这么做。请帮我们消灭这些可怕的合成体。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Let's hope you make it back alive."
msgstr "希望你活着回来。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Pretty understandable, I wouldn't want to stare down a few Salamanders "
"myself either."
msgstr "完全可以理解，我自己也不想面对几只火蜥蜴。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Try to avoid getting within melee range of those Salamanders, their legs can"
" send you flying."
msgstr "尽量避免进入那些火蜥蜴的近战范围，它们的腿能把你踢飞。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Are the Salamanders dead yet?"
msgstr "火蜥蜴干掉了吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"To be frank, I thought you would die, thanks for killing those beasts for "
"us."
msgstr "说实话，我以为你会死，谢谢你为我们消灭了那些野兽。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Eliminate the military patrol.'}'
#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Eliminate the military patrol."
msgstr "消灭军方巡逻队。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Okay, I think this will be the last task I entrust you with, not because I "
"doubt you, it's just that I think nothing can really top this. A scout has "
"detected a patrol of military bio-synthetics moving towards our base. It's "
"imperative that you take them out for us."
msgstr ""
"好吧，我想这是我委托给你的最后一个任务了，不是因为我怀疑你，只是我觉得没什么能比这更重要了。一名侦察兵发现一支军方生物合成体巡逻队正朝我们的基地移动。你必须为我们干掉他们。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "I entrust our safety to you, and you alone. Good luck!"
msgstr "我把我们的安全托付给你，只有你。祝你好运！"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "That's unfortunate, but so be it."
msgstr "那真不幸，但就这样吧。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"The military variants of the Newts and Salamanders often come equipped with "
"firearms, try to close the distance as soon as possible or snipe them from a"
" long distance."
msgstr "军用型蝾螈和火蜥蜴通常配备火器，尽量尽快拉近距离或从远处狙击它们。"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid "Are they dead dead yet?"
msgstr "它们死透了吗？"

#: .\NPCs\gkb_scrap_merchant.json
msgid ""
"This is amazing news! I think I owe you a particular gift. We found it at a "
"Chi Industries store some time ago, and never knew what to do with it."
msgstr "这消息太棒了！我想我欠你一份特别的礼物。我们之前在奇工业商店找到了它，一直不知道该怎么处理。"

#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\gkb_automaid_npc.json
msgid "Synthetic Maid"
msgstr "合成女仆"

#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\gkb_automaid_npc.json
msgid "A bio-synthetic maid."
msgstr "一个生物合成女仆。"

#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\gkb_automaid_npc.json
msgid "Chi Industries Synthetic Maid"
msgid_plural "Chi Industries Synthetic Maids"
msgstr[0] "奇工业合成女仆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chi Industries Synthetic Maid'}
#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\gkb_automaid_npc.json
msgid "A single-use item containing a synthetic maid for the user."
msgstr "一个一次性物品，内含一个供用户使用的合成女仆。"

#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\talk_automaid.json
msgid ""
"Hello, you are now the proud owner of a Chi Industries bio-synthetic unit, "
"please activate me at the soonest possible convenience."
msgstr "你好，你现在是奇工业生物合成单元的骄傲拥有者，请尽快激活我。"

#: .\NPCs\Artificial Gynoid\talk_automaid.json
msgid "please travel with me?"
msgstr "请和我一起旅行好吗？"
